title: Photography and Creative Imaging
description:
The Adobe MAX is an annual event held by Adobe Systems in North America, Europe and Japan. The purpose of the event is to promote the latest Adobe releases to those in the computer design and development industries.




URL: https://max.adobe.com/sessions/max-online/#track/photography


This package contains all sessions from the Photography & Creative Imaging category in MP4 format. Playable on every device including mobile devices.
